"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1147310","Department for Education","false","2019-10-07","<p>In 2017, the department spent £456.00 on first class rail travel and £1,870.70 on standard class ministerial rail travel. Further to this, the department spent £16,946.69 on business class air travel and £4,390.77 on economy class air travel. In total, the department spent £23,664.16 on ministerial travel.</p><p>In 2018, the department spent £2,399.70 on first class rail travel, £3,931.15 on standard class ministerial rail travel and £576.00 on premium economy Eurostar travel. Further to this, the department spent £15,994.92 on business class air travel and £3,481.64 on economy class air travel. In total, the department spent £26,383.41 on ministerial travel.</p><p> </p>","Chippenham","Michelle Donelan","292420","2019-10-07T06:30:33.47Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1147310/answer","Biography information for Michelle Donelan","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1147310/answer",,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1147310/answer",,,,,"60","Education","Education","2019-09-30","Department for Education: Travel","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Education, how much his Department spent on ministerial travel by (a) first class, (b) second class and (c) in total in 2017.","false","Biography information for Ruth Jones","Newport West","Ruth Jones","292410"
"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1147311","Department for International Development","false","2019-10-07","<p>Information on ministerial travel is not held centrally and could be provided only at disproportionate cost. However, the Department for International Development publishes data on ministerial overseas travel on a quarterly basis in arrears at the following link: <a href="https://eur02.safelinks.protection.outlook.com/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fdata.gov.uk%2Fdataset%2F8167ded1-0d4c-41ee-afd7-a6b39f2d1205%2Fministerial-gifts-hospitality-travel-and-meetings-with-external-organisations-in-the-department-for-international-development&amp;data=02%7C01%7Cc-hall%40dfid.gov.uk%7Cbc4ceee2d9b24abe718908d747da436f%7Ccdf709af1a184c74bd936d14a64d73b3%7C0%7C0%7C637056875067846048&amp;sdata=X2TVBGlaX31pKsemt6hHlpDHevduXOLHQaeSnrmmZbE%3D&amp;reserved=0" target="_blank">https://data.gov.uk/dataset/8167ded1-0d4c-41ee-afd7-a6b39f2d1205/ministerial-gifts-hospitality-travel-and-meetings-with-external-organisations-in-the-department-for-international-development</a></p><p>We do not routinely publish any national travel costs for Ministers.</p>","Richmond Park","Zac Goldsmith","292421","2019-10-07T16:19:21.097Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1147311/answer","Biography information for Zac Goldsmith","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1147311/answer",,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1147311/answer",,,,,"20","International Development","International Development","2019-09-30","Department for International Development: Travel","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for International Development, how much his Department spent on ministerial travel by (a) first class, (b) second class and (c) in total in 2017.","false","Biography information for Ruth Jones","Newport West","Ruth Jones","292411"
